Sa’alo’alo (河川)

Kasa’alo’alo o karomakatan no nanom, kafesa’ay han ko sowal, masonol tayra i riyar, fanaw ato roma ’alo. Sakimatiniay i, o ’alo ’ayaw no malananom, masonol i sera ato malalahod. O mimingay ’alo o cici’, ’alo ato sa’owac (stream, creek and brook). Tarawadaw i o kadado’edoan, kasaopoan no masonolay nanom; palolol to la’enoay no sera ato nemnem a nanom; misopeday o li^etecay ato so^eda parocek to palapala.{{stub}}
